msgctxt "2856_Rio"
msgid "Akiyama-san!?"
msgstr "¿¡Akiyama-san!?"

msgctxt "2868_Player"
msgid "Sorry to keep you waiting."
msgstr "Lamento hacerle esperar."

msgctxt "2880_Rio"
msgid "Hold on, is that person with you? I thought this was gonna be a date..."
msgstr "Hold on, is that person with you? I thought this was gonna be a date..."

msgctxt "2892_Player"
msgid "I thought we were going to be alone..."
msgstr "Pensé que tendríamos una cita, solo nosotros dos..."

msgctxt "2904_Player"
msgid "......"
msgstr "......"

msgctxt "2916_Rio"
msgid "Why don't you meet me back here when you're alone?"
msgstr "Why don't you meet me back here when you're alone?"

msgctxt "2928_Rio"
msgid "Akiyama-san!?"
msgstr "¿¡Akiyama-san!?"

msgctxt "2940_Player"
msgid "Sorry to keep you waiting."
msgstr "Lamento hacerle esperar."

msgctxt "2952_Rio"
msgid "What are you doing with all that? Were you going to work during our date or something?"
msgstr "What are you doing with all that? Were you going to work during our date or something?"

msgctxt "2964_Player"
msgid "No, no, of course not."
msgstr "No, no, of course not."

msgctxt "2976_Rio"
msgid "I'll be here. Try to be quick."
msgstr "I'll be here. Try to be quick."

