msgctxt "3348_Photographer"
msgid "Rio!"
msgstr "¡Rio!"

msgctxt "3360_Rio"
msgid "Oh! It's my photographer!"
msgstr "Oh! It's my photographer!"

msgctxt "3372_Photographer"
msgid "Oh, wow. I knew you were beautiful in a dress, but you look amazing in that outfit, too!"
msgstr "Oh, wow. I knew you were beautiful in a dress, but you look amazing in that outfit, too!"

msgctxt "3384_Rio"
msgid "You're such a flatterer! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"
msgstr "You're such a flatterer! <Color:7>♥<Color:Default>"

msgctxt "3396_Photographer"
msgid "But it's true! And by the way, have you thought about what we discussed?"
msgstr "But it's true! And by the way, have you thought about what we discussed?"

msgctxt "3408_Rio"
msgid "Oh, uh. Yes... The pin-up model job, right?"
msgstr "Oh, uh. Yes... The pin-up model job, right?"

msgctxt "3420_Rio"
msgid "You said you knew someone at an agency?"
msgstr "You said you knew someone at an agency?"

msgctxt "3432_Photographer"
msgid "That's right. You'd be just perfect for that kind of work."
msgstr "That's right. You'd be just perfect for that kind of work."

msgctxt "3444_Rio"
msgid "Um... Could I get a little more time to think about it?"
msgstr "Um... Could I get a little more time to think about it?"

msgctxt "3456_Photographer"
msgid "Well, the agency can't wait forever. You need to make up your mind as soon as possible."
msgstr "Well, the agency can't wait forever. You need to make up your mind as soon as possible."

msgctxt "3480_Akiyama"
msgid "That was the guy you were telling me about?"
msgstr "That was the guy you were telling me about?"

msgctxt "3492_Rio"
msgid "Yeah..."
msgstr "Sí..."

msgctxt "3504_Akiyama"
msgid "Looks like you're taking this offer seriously."
msgstr "Looks like you're taking this offer seriously."

msgctxt "3516_Rio"
msgid "I am... But I haven't made up my mind yet."
msgstr "I am... But I haven't made up my mind yet."

msgctxt "3528_Akiyama"
msgid "Well, you shouldn't rush your decision. Take your time and think it over."
msgstr "Well, you shouldn't rush your decision. Take your time and think it over."

msgctxt "3540_Rio"
msgid "I already am."
msgstr "Ya lo estoy haciendo."

msgctxt "3552_Rio"
msgid "So... Where are you taking me today?"
msgstr "Entonces... ¿A dónde me llevará hoy?"

msgctxt "3564_Player"
msgid "(What should we do?)"
msgstr "(¿Qué deberíamos hacer...?)"

msgctxt "3588_Player"
