msgid "Yakiniku? Now that I think of it, I am kinda hungry."
msgstr "Yakiniku? Now that I think of it, I am kinda hungry."

msgctxt "3672_Rio"
msgid "Okay, let's go."
msgstr "Bueno, vamos."

